channel.title: Printer Settings :: CID guide website
channel.description: Now that you have your print set up, click the Printer button in the top left. Choose Printer Under the choose printer section, select the dropdown and select Form 3/3+. Then underneath should appear a row named AzureGoshawk which you should select. Choose Material Select whatever material is currently loaded in the printer. Choose Layer Thickness Layer thickness will change how fast the file prints as well as the resolution of the product.
